### Barrel Update

[index.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/resources/index.ts) now also exports `employee.service` and `user.service`.

### Name Clash Fix

[ReportTemplate](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/types/reports.ts#6-14) in [reports.service.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/resources/reports.service.ts) renamed to [ReportTemplateSummary](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/resources/reports.service.ts#15-22) to avoid conflict with the canonical [ReportTemplate](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/types/reports.ts#6-14) in [types/reports.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/types/reports.ts) (which describes the template JSON structure with sections/filters/layout).

## Pattern Applied

Every service method that reads data from the API now follows:

```typescript
const raw = await apiClient.get<unknown>('/endpoint');
return normalizeKeys<TargetType>(raw);
```

## Not Touched

- [lib/api.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/lib/api.ts) (fetch-based) — 10+ consumers in stores/components/hooks
- Pages, stores, components, config, routing
- Backend, infrastructure, deployment

